{Grimlock}

    The blasts struck grimlock in the chest singing the metallic plating of
his chest, stopping the fire for a moment. "Me Grimlock say that all you
got? Grimlock transform!"

   Shifting the metallic t-rex transformed into his hulking robot mode,
energy blade in one hand, dual laser cannon in the other, raising his arm he
squeezed both triggers firing off a double volley of energy blasts at the
flying bot.
